      "claudeProjectionRoot": ".claude/skills",
      "notes": "The /flow engine bundle. Its skills live canonically under `.agents/flow/skills/<name>` (NOT the flat `.agents/skills/<name>`), and project into `.claude/skills/<name>` as per-skill symlinks — same mechanism and entry shape as `sharedSkills`. Commands stay Claude-native in `.claude/commands/flow/` (no repo-local command format for Cursor/Codex) and the unified loop hook stays in `.claude/settings.json` (hookPolicies projection: none). The sync mechanism is per-skill (explicit entries; no glob), so each skill added under `.agents/flow/skills/` in P1 MUST add a matching entry to `skills` below. Empty in P0 — the skills dir holds only `.gitkeep`, so no symlinks are created yet.",
